Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.04,0:16:08.76,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\an7\fad(300,300)\shad0\1a&H00&\c&H000000&\blur3\bord3\3c&HFFFFFF&}啊 未来的路 带领我走向您
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.76,0:16:21.61,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\an7\fad(300,300)\shad0\1a&H00&\c&H000000&\blur3\bord3\3c&HFFFFFF&}清风徐徐 掀开点滴回忆
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.61,0:16:34.44,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\an7\fad(300,300)\shad0\1a&H00&\c&H000000&\blur3\bord3\3c&HFFFFFF&}啊 过去种种 绽放温暖光芒
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.44,0:16:47.20,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\an7\fad(300,300)\shad0\1a&H00&\c&H000000&\blur3\bord3\3c&HFFFFFF&}您是这个世界上 最理解我们的人
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.20,0:16:59.23,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\an7\fad(300,300)\shad0\1a&H00&\c&H000000&\blur3\bord3\3c&HFFFFFF&}老师的谆谆教诲 今后也将为我们指点迷津
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.23,0:17:08.93,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\an7\fad(300,300)\shad0\1a&H00&\c&H000000&\blur3\bord3\3c&HFFFFFF&}点点樱花 悄然凋零
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.83,0:17:24.71,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\an7\fad(300,300)\shad0\1a&H00&\c&H000000&\blur3\bord3\3c&HFFFFFF&}属于我们的时间 止不住回放
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.71,0:17:38.40,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\an7\fad(300,300)\shad0\1a&H00&\c&H000000&\blur3\bord3\3c&HFFFFFF&}心中虽明了 却无法自已 只能望着这片天空
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.40,0:17:50.35,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\an7\fad(300,300)\shad0\1a&H00&\c&H000000&\blur3\bord3\3c&HFFFFFF&}在这离别时刻 向您道谢 表达敬爱
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.35,0:17:59.95,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\an7\fad(300,300)\shad0\1a&H00&\c&H000000&\blur3\bord3\3c&HFFFFFF&}我们将带着您的鼓舞
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.95,0:18:06.45,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\an7\fad(300,300)\shad0\1a&H00&\c&H000000&\blur3\bord3\3c&HFFFFFF&}唱响这首启程之歌
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.80,0:18:28.77,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\an7\fad(300,300)\shad0\1a&H00&\c&H000000&\blur3\bord3\3c&HFFFFFF&}属于我们的时间 渐渐远去的校舍
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.77,0:18:42.41,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\an7\fad(300,300)\shad0\1a&H00&\c&H000000&\blur3\bord3\3c&HFFFFFF&}珍贵的友人 和人生导师 全都属于那里
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.41,0:18:54.37,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\an7\fad(300,300)\shad0\1a&H00&\c&H000000&\blur3\bord3\3c&HFFFFFF&}在这离别时刻 即将毕业的我们
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.37,0:19:03.80,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\an7\fad(300,300)\shad0\1a&H00&\c&H000000&\blur3\bord3\3c&HFFFFFF&}将对老师的感谢之情
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.80,0:19:11.32,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\an7\fad(300,300)\shad0\1a&H00&\c&H000000&\blur3\bord3\3c&HFFFFFF&}化作这首启程之歌
