Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.57,0:21:37.54,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur1\fad(200,284)}叶间阳光 轻轻洒进偌大的窗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.54,0:21:48.14,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur1\fad(200,284)}相遇那天 如今想来恍若隔世
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.51,0:21:55.18,ED-CN,,0,0,1,,{\blur1\fad(200,284)}回忆幕幕在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.18,0:21:59.27,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,284)}点滴汇聚暖心田
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.31,0:22:06.45,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,284)}小小房间 心心相连
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.45,0:22:12.03,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,400)}将一切静静诉说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.03,0:22:18.21,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}当这个季节到来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.21,0:22:24.88,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,284)}纵想寻你千百遍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.88,0:22:30.22,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}奈何你已不在世间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.22,0:22:35.77,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,284)}我会永远铭记着你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.77,0:22:41.81,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,400)}直到重逢那天…
